<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/919421-i-am-a-little-over-100-pages-into-this">I am a little over 100 pages into this book &amp; really struggling to feel invested in the characters or the story. I can certainly appreciate Vargas Llosa&#39;s writing for it&#39;s skill and polish, but I find myself getting bored before I get to the end of each chapter. Does the tone and/or pace pick up at any point, or is it this dense the whole way through? I am not afraid of long, dense tomes but I can&#39;t get into this one!</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
